Crazy Snakes
+ Author: Paul Gatterdam
+ Version: 0.2
+ Game Engine: Unity3D v4.0
+ Release Date: 1/13/2013

Game Rules
-------------
Crazy Snakes is a mashup of Snake and multiplayer functionality.

Right click anywhere on the map to move in that direction.

Eat green food pellets to grow!

Try not to run into walls or other players.


